&#39;</a> (feat. <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-beatty">Ryan Beatty</a> ).</p><p> Last year, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/easy-life-share-new-kevin-abstract-collaboration-dear-miss-holloway-3233716">Abstract collaborated with Easy Life on their track &#39;Dear Miss Holloway&#39;</a> before <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2022-easy-life-kevin-abstract-interview-3255896">joining the band on stage at Glastonbury Festival 2022</a> .</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-brockhampton-play-their-final-concert-at-las-fonda-theatre-3352191">Brockhampton played their final show last November in Los Angeles</a> after dropping their last albums <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/brockhampton-the-family-review-kevin-abstract-3351690">&#39;The Family&#39;</a> and &#39;TM&#39;, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brockhampton-farewell-fans-with-new-album-tm-announce-live-streamed-final-performance-3351528">the latter of which arrived without any prior announcement</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kevin-abstract-previews-new-rock-album-first-show-six-years-3506653">Kevin Abstract previews new rock album at first show in six years</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
